assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Beijing Dataway Horizon Co.,Ltd. provides data analysis and decision support services in China. It offers data services, including Youzhengtong, an automated comprehensive data service platform; You Caitong, which include full-process performance evaluation and data application support for the implementation of budget performance management by local financial departments and budget departments; Youshangtong comprising urban insight, monitoring, work supervision, enterprise demand mining, and cases and cutting edge policy knowledge sharing services; and Youshuitong services, such as automatic demand data collection, intelligent analysis of multi-source data, and visualize and display services. The company also provides data services for the commercial fields, including numerical benefits, such as customer experience optimization, and company's service management and response capabilities optimization services; Shuyoupin comprises product experience optimization services; and omni-channel management optimization services. In addition, it offers commodity operation systems; super store manager, a terminal store efficiency system; intelligent public security systems; and city transportation center systems. Beijing Dataway Horizon Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1993 and is based in Beijing, China.
